tachyon.worker.block.meta

Class StorageDirView

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.worker.block.meta.StorageDirView

  • public final class StorageDirView
extends Object
    This class is a wrapper of StorageDir to provide more limited access and a filtered list of blocks.

    • Constructor Summary
